{"data":[{"name":"53:1","price":"क़सम है तारे की जब वह गिरे!","arabic":"وَٱلنَّجۡمِ إِذَا هَوَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4785,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-najmi idhā hawā ","translations":["By the star","when","it goes down","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-najmi","idhā","hawā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2350],[2,2350,2980],[3,2980,3855]]}},{"name":"53:2","price":"तुम्हारा साथी न तो रास्ते से भटका है और न ही गलत रास्ते पर चला है।","arabic":"مَا ضَلَّ صَاحِبُكُمۡ وَمَا غَوَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4786,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"mā ḍalla ṣāḥibukum wamā ghawā ","translations":["Not","has strayed","your companion","and not","has he erred","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["mā","ḍalla","ṣāḥibukum","wamā","ghawā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,420],[2,420,1170],[3,1170,2600],[4,2600,3320],[5,3320,4125]]}},{"name":"53:3","price":"और न वह अपनी इच्छा से बोलता है।","arabic":"وَمَا يَنطِقُ عَنِ ٱلۡهَوَىٰٓ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4787,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā yanṭiqu ʿani al-hawā ","translations":["And not","he speaks","from","the desire","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","yanṭiqu","ʿani","al-hawā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,720],[2,720,2560],[3,2560,2930],[4,2930,4025]]}},{"name":"53:4","price":"वह तो केवल वह़्य है, जो उतारी जाती है।","arabic":"إِنۡ هُوَ إِلَّا وَحۡيٞ يُوحَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4788,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"in huwa illā waḥyun yūḥā ","translations":["Not","it","(is) except","a revelation","revealed","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["in","huwa","illā","waḥyun","yūḥā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,470],[2,470,800],[3,800,1800],[4,1800,2550],[5,2550,4355]]}},{"name":"53:5","price":"उसे बहुत मज़ूबत शक्तियों वाले (फ़रिश्ते)[1] ने सिखाया है।","arabic":"عَلَّمَهُۥ شَدِيدُ ٱلۡقُوَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4789,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"1. इससे अभिप्राय जिबरील (अलैहिस्सलाम) हैं, जो वह़्य लाते थे।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿallamahu shadīdu al-quwā ","translations":["Has taught him","the (one) mighty","(in) power","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿallamahu","shadīdu","al-quwā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1310],[2,1310,2570],[3,2570,3445]]}},{"name":"53:6","price":"जो बड़ा बलशाली है। फिर वह बुलंद हुआ (अपने असली रूप में प्रकट हुआ)।","arabic":"ذُو مِرَّةٖ فَٱسۡتَوَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4790,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"dhū mirratin fa-is'tawā ","translations":["Possessor of soundness","Possessor of soundness","And he rose","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["dhū","mirratin","fa-is'tawā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,560],[2,560,1950],[3,1950,3835]]}},{"name":"53:7","price":"जबकि वह आकाश के सबसे ऊँचे क्षितिज (पूर्वी किनारे) पर था।","arabic":"وَهُوَ بِٱلۡأُفُقِ ٱلۡأَعۡلَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4791,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wahuwa bil-ufuqi al-aʿlā ","translations":["While he","(was) in the horizon ","the highest","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["wahuwa","bil-ufuqi","al-aʿlā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,660],[2,660,1850],[3,1850,3115]]}},{"name":"53:8","price":"फिर वह निकट हुआ और उतर आया।","arabic":"ثُمَّ دَنَا فَتَدَلَّىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4792,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma danā fatadallā ","translations":["Then","he approached","and came down","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","danā","fatadallā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1230],[2,1230,2000],[3,2000,3475]]}},{"name":"53:9","price":"फिर वह दो धनुषों की दूरी पर था, या उससे भी निकट।","arabic":"فَكَانَ قَابَ قَوۡسَيۡنِ أَوۡ أَدۡنَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4793,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"fakāna qāba qawsayni aw adnā ","translations":["And was","(at) a distance","(of) two bow-(lengths)","or","nearer","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["fakāna","qāba","qawsayni","aw","adnā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,960],[2,960,1640],[3,1640,2850],[4,2850,3250],[5,3250,4235]]}},{"name":"53:10","price":"फिर उसने अल्लाह के बंदे[2] की ओर वह़्य की, जो भी वह़्य की।","arabic":"فَأَوۡحَىٰٓ إِلَىٰ عَبۡدِهِۦ مَآ أَوۡحَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4794,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"2. अर्थात मुहम्मद (सल्लल्लाहु अलैहि व सल्लम) की ओर। इन आयतों में नबी (सल्लल्लाहु अलैहि व सल्लम) के जिबरील (फरिश्ते) को उनके वास्तविक रूप में दो बार देखने का वर्णन है। आयशा (रज़ियल्लाहु अन्हा) ने कहा : जो कहे कि मुह़म्मद (सल्लल्लहु अलैहि व सल्लम) ने अल्लाह को देखा है, तो वह झूठा है। और जो कहे कि आप कल (भविष्य) की बात जानते थे, तो वह झूठा है। तथा जो कहे कि आप ने धर्म की कुछ बातें छिपा लीं, तो वह झूठा है। किंतु आपने जिबरील (अलैहिस्सलाम) को उनके रूप में दो बार देखा। (बुख़ारी : 4855) इब्ने मसऊद ने कहा कि आपने जिबरील को देखा जिनके छह सौ पंख थे। (बुख़ारी : 4856)","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-awḥā ilā ʿabdihi mā awḥā ","translations":["So he revealed","to","His slave","what","he revealed","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-awḥā","ilā","ʿabdihi","mā","awḥā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2510],[2,2510,3160],[3,3160,4330],[4,4330,4510],[5,4510,5960],[6,5960,7045]]}},{"name":"53:11","price":"दिल ने झूठ नहीं बोला, जो कुछ उसने देखा।","arabic":"مَا كَذَبَ ٱلۡفُؤَادُ مَا رَأَىٰٓ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4795,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"mā kadhaba al-fuādu mā raā ","translations":["Not","lied","the heart","what","it saw","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["mā","kadhaba","al-fuādu","mā","raā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,480],[2,480,1150],[3,1150,2370],[4,2370,2830],[5,2830,3565]]}},{"name":"53:12","price":"फिर क्या तुम उससे उसपर झगड़ते हो, जो वह देखता है?","arabic":"أَفَتُمَٰرُونَهُۥ عَلَىٰ مَا يَرَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4796,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"afatumārūnahu ʿalā mā yarā ","translations":["Then will you dispute with him","about","what","he saw","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["afatumārūnahu","ʿalā","mā","yarā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2320],[2,2320,3100],[3,3100,3570],[4,3570,4875]]}},{"name":"53:13","price":"हालाँकि, निश्चित रूप से उसने उसे एक और बार उतरते हुए भी देखा है।","arabic":"وَلَقَدۡ رَءَاهُ نَزۡلَةً أُخۡرَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4797,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"walaqad raāhu nazlatan ukh'rā ","translations":["And certainly","he saw him","(in) descent","another","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["walaqad","raāhu","nazlatan","ukh'rā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,850],[2,850,1810],[3,1810,2950],[4,2950,4395]]}},{"name":"53:14","price":"सिदरतुल-मुनतहा'[3]  के पास।","arabic":"عِندَ سِدۡرَةِ ٱلۡمُنتَهَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4798,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"3. 'सिदरतुल मुनतहा', यह छठे या सातवें आकाश पर बैरी का एक वृक्ष है। जिस तक धरती की चीज़ पहुँचती है। तथा ऊपर की चीज़ उतरती है। (सह़ीह़ मुस्लिम : 173)","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿinda sid'rati al-muntahā ","translations":["Near","(the) Lote Tree","(of) the utmost boundary","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿinda","sid'rati","al-muntahā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1410],[2,1410,2410],[3,2410,4665]]}},{"name":"53:15","price":"उसी के पास 'जन्नतुल मावा' (शाश्वत स्वर्ग) है।","arabic":"عِندَهَا جَنَّةُ ٱلۡمَأۡوَىٰٓ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4799,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿindahā jannatu al-mawā ","translations":["Near it","(is the) Garden","(of) Abode","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿindahā","jannatu","al-mawā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1930],[2,1930,3670],[3,3670,4965]]}},{"name":"53:16","price":"जब सिदरा पर छा रहा था, जो कुछ छा रहा था।[4]","arabic":"إِذۡ يَغۡشَى ٱلسِّدۡرَةَ مَا يَغۡشَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4800,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"4. ह़दीस में है कि वह सोने के पतिंगे थे। (सह़ीह़ मुस्लिम : 173)","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"idh yaghshā al-sid'rata mā yaghshā ","translations":["When","covered","the Lote Tree","what","covers","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["idh","yaghshā","al-sid'rata","mā","yaghshā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,490],[2,490,1090],[3,1090,2330],[4,2330,2780],[5,2780,3835]]}},{"name":"53:17","price":"न निगाह इधर-उधर हुई और न सीमा से आगे बढ़ी।","arabic":"مَا زَاغَ ٱلۡبَصَرُ وَمَا طَغَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4801,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"mā zāgha al-baṣaru wamā ṭaghā ","translations":["Not","swerved","the sight","and not","it transgressed","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["mā","zāgha","al-baṣaru","wamā","ṭaghā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,500],[2,500,1220],[3,1220,2150],[4,2150,2630],[5,2630,4275]]}},{"name":"53:18","price":"निःसंदेह उसने अपने पालनहार की कुछ बहुत बड़ी निशानियाँ[5] देखीं।","arabic":"لَقَدۡ رَأَىٰ مِنۡ ءَايَٰتِ رَبِّهِ ٱلۡكُبۡرَىٰٓ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4802,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"5. इसमें मे'राज की रात आप (सल्लल्लाहु अलैहि व सल्लम) के आकाशों में अल्लाह की निशानियाँ देखने का वर्णन है।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"laqad raā min āyāti rabbihi al-kub'rā ","translations":["Certainly","he saw","of","(the) Signs","(of) his Lord","the Greatest","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["laqad","raā","min","āyāti","rabbihi","al-kub'rā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,650],[2,650,1390],[3,1390,1830],[4,1830,3160],[5,3160,3980],[6,3980,5725]]}},{"name":"53:19","price":"फिर क्या तुमने लात और उज़्ज़ा को देखा।","arabic":"أَفَرَءَيۡتُمُ ٱللَّٰتَ وَٱلۡعُزَّىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4803,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"afara-aytumu al-lāta wal-ʿuzā ","translations":["So have you seen","the Lat","and the Uzza","(19)"],"transliterationArr":["afara-aytumu","al-lāta","wal-ʿuzā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1630],[2,1630,2720],[3,2720,4195]]}},{"name":"53:20","price":"तथा तीसरी एक और (मूर्ति) मनात को?[6]","arabic":"وَمَنَوٰةَ ٱلثَّالِثَةَ ٱلۡأُخۡرَىٰٓ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4804,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"6. लात, उज़्ज़ा और मनात ये तीनों मक्का के मुश्रिकों की देवियों के नाम हैं। और अर्थ यह है कि क्या इनकी भी कोई वास्तविकता है?","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wamanata al-thālithata al-ukh'rā ","translations":["And Manat","the third","the other","(20)"],"transliterationArr":["wamanata","al-thālithata","al-ukh'rā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1160],[2,1160,2600],[3,2600,4525]]}},{"name":"53:21","price":"क्या तुम्हारे लिए पुत्र हैं और उस (अल्लाह) के लिए पुत्रियाँ?","arabic":"أَلَكُمُ ٱلذَّكَرُ وَلَهُ ٱلۡأُنثَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4805,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"alakumu al-dhakaru walahu al-unthā ","translations":["Is for you","the male","and for Him","the female","(21)"],"transliterationArr":["alakumu","al-dhakaru","walahu","al-unthā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,870],[2,870,1910],[3,1910,2590],[4,2590,4775]]}},{"name":"53:22","price":"तब तो यह बड़ा अन्यायपूर्ण बँटवारा है।","arabic":"تِلۡكَ إِذٗا قِسۡمَةٞ ضِيزَىٰٓ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4806,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"til'ka idhan qis'matun ḍīzā ","translations":["This","then","(is) a division","unfair","(22)"],"transliterationArr":["til'ka","idhan","qis'matun","ḍīzā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,660],[2,660,2180],[3,2180,4430],[4,4430,5565]]}},{"name":"53:23","price":"ये (मूर्तियाँ) कुछ नामों के सिवा कुछ भी नहीं हैं, जो तुमने तथा तुम्हारे बाप-दादा ने रख लिए हैं। अल्लाह ने इनका कोई प्रमाण नहीं उतारा है। ये लोग केवल अटकल[7] के और उन चीज़ों के पीछे चल रहे हैं जो उनके दिल चाहते हैं। जबकि निःसंदेह उनके पास उनके पालनहार की ओर से मार्गदर्शन आ चुका है।","arabic":"إِنۡ هِيَ إِلَّآ أَسۡمَآءٞ سَمَّيۡتُمُوهَآ أَنتُمۡ وَءَابَآؤُكُم مَّآ أَنزَلَ ٱللَّهُ بِهَا مِن سُلۡطَٰنٍۚ إِن يَتَّبِعُونَ إِلَّا ٱلظَّنَّ وَمَا تَهۡوَى ٱلۡأَنفُسُۖ وَلَقَدۡ جَآءَهُم مِّن رَّبِّهِمُ ٱلۡهُدَىٰٓ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4807,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"7. मुश्रिक अपनी मूर्तियों को अल्लाह की पुत्रियाँ कहकर उनकी पूजा करते थे, जिसका यहाँ खंडन किया जा रहा है।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"in hiya illā asmāon sammaytumūhā antum waābāukum mā anzala al-lahu bihā min sul'ṭānin in yattabiʿūna illā al-ẓana wamā tahwā al-anfusu walaqad jāahum min rabbihimu al-hudā ","translations":["Not","they","(are) except","names","you have named them","you","and your forefathers","not","has Allah sent down","has Allah sent down","for it","any","authority","Not","they follow","except","assumption","and what","desire","the(ir) souls","And certainly","has come to them","from","their Lord","the guidance","(23)"],"transliterationArr":["in","hiya","illā","asmāon","sammaytumūhā","antum","waābāukum","mā","anzala","al-lahu","bihā","min","sul'ṭānin","in","yattabiʿūna","illā","al-ẓana","wamā","tahwā","al-anfusu","walaqad","jāahum","min","rabbihimu","al-hudā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,500],[2,500,930],[3,930,3080],[4,3080,6460],[5,6460,9370],[6,9370,14280],[7,14280,15980],[8,15980,19500],[9,19500,21410],[10,21410,22810],[11,22810,23910],[12,23910,24560],[13,24560,24920],[14,24920,25760],[15,25760,29440],[16,29440,30390],[17,30390,31870],[18,31870,32570],[19,32570,34170],[20,34170,34810],[21,34810,35510],[22,35510,37820],[23,37820,39200],[24,39200,42030],[25,42030,43140],[26,43140,44520],[27,44520,45645]]}},{"name":"53:24","price":"क्या मनुष्य को वह मिल जाएगा, जिसकी वह कामना करे?","arabic":"أَمۡ لِلۡإِنسَٰنِ مَا تَمَنَّىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4808,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"am lil'insāni mā tamannā ","translations":["Or","(is) for man","what","he wishes","(24)"],"transliterationArr":["am","lil'insāni","mā","tamannā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,430],[2,430,2850],[3,2850,3250],[4,3250,5335]]}},{"name":"53:25","price":"(नहीं, ऐसा नहीं है) क्योंकि आख़िरत और दुनिया अल्लाह ही के अधिकार में है।","arabic":"فَلِلَّهِ ٱلۡأٓخِرَةُ وَٱلۡأُولَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4809,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"falillahi al-ākhiratu wal-ūlā ","translations":["But for Allah","(is) the last","and the first","(25)"],"transliterationArr":["falillahi","al-ākhiratu","wal-ūlā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1330],[2,1330,2790],[3,2790,4145]]}},{"name":"53:26","price":"और आकाशों में कितने ही फ़रिश्ते हैं कि उनकी सिफ़ारिश कुछ लाभ नहीं देती, परंतु इसके पश्चात कि अल्लाह अनुमति दे जिसके लिए चाहे तथा (जिसे) पसंद करे।[8]","arabic":"۞ وَكَم مِّن مَّلَكٖ فِي ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ لَا تُغۡنِي شَفَٰعَتُهُمۡ شَيۡـًٔا إِلَّا مِنۢ بَعۡدِ أَن يَأۡذَنَ ٱللَّهُ لِمَن يَشَآءُ وَيَرۡضَىٰٓ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4810,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"8. अरब के मुश्रिक यह समझते थे कि यदि हम फ़रिश्तों की पूजा करेंगे, तो वे अल्लाह से सिफ़ारिश करके हमें यातना से मुक्त करा देंगे। इसी का खंडन यहाँ किया जा रहा है।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wakam min malakin fī al-samāwāti lā tugh'nī shafāʿatuhum shayan illā min baʿdi an yadhana al-lahu liman yashāu wayarḍā ","translations":["And how many","of","(the) Angels","in","the heavens","not","will avail","their intercession","anything","except","after","after","[that]","Allah has given permission","Allah has given permission","for whom","He wills","and approves","(26)"],"transliteration