"And not","for them","about it","any","knowledge","Not","they follow","but","assumption","And indeed","the assumption","(does) not","avail","against","the truth","anything","(28)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","lahum","bihi","min","ʿil'min","in","yattabiʿūna","illā","al-ẓana","wa-inna","al-ẓana","lā","yugh'nī","mina","al-ḥaqi","shayan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,670],[2,670,2209],[3,2209,2920],[4,2920,3350],[5,3350,4520],[6,4520,5740],[7,5740,7240],[8,7240,7870],[9,7870,9650],[10,9650,11000],[11,11000,12350],[12,12350,12820],[13,12820,13730],[14,13730,14170],[15,14170,15090],[16,15090,16145]]}},{"name":"53:29","price":"अतः आप उससे मुँह फेर लें, जिसने हमारी नसीहत से मुँह मोड़ लिया और जिसने दुनिया के जीवन के सिवा कुछ नहीं चाहा।","arabic":"فَأَعۡرِضۡ عَن مَّن تَوَلَّىٰ عَن ذِكۡرِنَا وَلَمۡ يُرِدۡ إِلَّا ٱلۡحَيَوٰةَ ٱلدُّنۡيَا","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4813,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-aʿriḍ ʿan man tawallā ʿan dhik'rinā walam yurid illā al-ḥayata al-dun'yā ","translations":["So turn away","from","(him) who","turns away","from","Our Reminder","and not","he desires","except","the life","(of) the world","(29)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-aʿriḍ","ʿan","man","tawallā","ʿan","dhik'rinā","walam","yurid","illā","al-ḥayata","al-dun'yā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1080],[2,1080,1370],[3,1370,2900],[4,2900,4050],[5,4050,5080],[6,5080,6190],[7,6190,6870],[8,6870,7560],[9,7560,8160],[10,8160,9310],[11,9310,10535]]}},{"name":"53:30","price":"यही उनके ज्ञान की सीमा है। निश्चित रूप से आपका पालनहार ही उसे अधिक जानने वाला है, जो उसके मार्ग से भटक गया और वही उसे भी ज़्यादा जानने वाला है, जो सीधे मार्ग पर चला।","arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ مَبۡلَغُهُم مِّنَ ٱلۡعِلۡمِۚ إِنَّ رَبَّكَ هُوَ أَعۡلَمُ بِمَن ضَلَّ عَن سَبِيلِهِۦ وَهُوَ أَعۡلَمُ بِمَنِ ٱهۡتَدَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4814,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"dhālika mablaghuhum mina a