Najm"],"ayahNumber":4819,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"11. इस आयत में जो परंपरागत धर्म को मोक्ष का साधन समझता है उससे कहा जा रहा है कि क्या वह जानता है कि प्रलय के दिन इतने ही से सफल हो जाएगा? जबकि नबी (सल्लल्लाहु अलैहि व सल्लम) वह़्य के आधार पर जो प्रस्तुत कर रहे हैं, वही सत्य है। और अल्लाह की वह़्य ही परोक्ष के ज्ञान का साधन है।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"aʿindahu ʿil'mu al-ghaybi fahuwa yarā ","translations":["Is with him","(the) knowledge","(of) the unseen","so he","sees","(35)"],"transliterationArr":["aʿindahu","ʿil'mu","al-ghaybi","fahuwa","yarā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1860],[2,1860,2490],[3,2490,3390],[4,3390,4130],[5,4130,5345]]}},{"name":"53:36","price":"या उसे उन बातों की सूचना नहीं दी गई, जो मूसा के ग्रंथों में हैं?","arabic":"أَمۡ لَمۡ يُنَبَّأۡ بِمَا فِي صُحُفِ مُوسَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4820,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"am lam yunabba bimā fī ṣuḥufi mūsā ","translations":["Or","not","he was informed","with what","(was) in","(the) Scriptures","(of) Musa","(36)"],"transliterationArr":["am","lam","yunabba","bimā","fī","ṣuḥufi","mūsā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,370],[2,370,830],[3,830,1840],[4,1840,2510],[5,2510,2960],[6,2960,3710],[7,3710,4725]]}},{"name":"53:37","price":"और इबराहीम के (ग्रंथों में), जिसने (कर्तव्य) पूरा किया।","arabic":"وَإِبۡرَٰهِيمَ ٱلَّذِي وَفَّىٰٓ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4821,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-ib'rāhīma alladhī waffā ","translations":["And Ibrahim","who","fulfilled","(37)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-ib'rāhīma","alladhī","waffā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1670],[2,1670,2630],[3,2630,3625]]}},{"name":"53:38","price":"कि कोई बोझ उठाने वाला किसी दूसरे का बोझ नहीं उठाएगा।","arabic":"أَلَّا تَزِرُ وَازِرَةٞ وِزۡرَ أُخۡرَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4822,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"allā taziru wāziratun wiz'ra ukh'rā ","translations":["That not","will bear","a bearer of burdens","(the) burden","(of) another","(38)"],"transliterationArr":["allā","taziru","wāziratun","wiz'ra","ukh'rā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,1480],[3,1480,3510],[4,3510,4200],[5,4200,5645]]}},{"name":"53:39","price":"और यह कि मनुष्य के लिए केवल वही है, जिसके लिए उसने प्रयास किया।","arabic":"وَأَن لَّيۡسَ لِلۡإِنسَٰنِ إِلَّا مَا سَعَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4823,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-an laysa lil'insāni illā mā saʿā ","translations":["And that","is not","for man","except","what","he strives (for)","(39)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-an","laysa","lil'insāni","illā","mā","saʿā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,450],[2,450,1240],[3,1240,3650],[4,3650,4560],[5,4560,4950],[6,4950,5805]]}},{"name":"53:40","price":"और यह कि निश्चय उसका प्रयास शीघ्र ही देखा जाएगा।","arabic":"وَأَنَّ سَعۡيَهُۥ سَوۡفَ يُرَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4824,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-anna saʿyahu sawfa yurā ","translations":["And that","his striving","will soon","be seen","(40)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-anna","saʿyahu","sawfa","yurā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1300],[2,1300,2420],[3,2420,3180],[4,3180,4395]]}},{"name":"53:41","price":"फिर उसे उसका पूरा प्रतिफल दिया जाएगा।","arabic":"ثُمَّ يُجۡزَىٰهُ ٱلۡجَزَآءَ ٱلۡأَوۡفَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4825,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma yuj'zāhu al-jazāa al-awfā ","translations":["Then","he will be recompensed for it","the recompense","the fullest","(41)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","yuj'zāhu","al-jazāa","al-awfā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1020],[2,1020,2220],[3,2220,4860],[4,4860,6195]]}},{"name":"53:42","price":"और यह कि निःसंदेह आपके पालनहार ही की ओर अंततः पहुँचना है।","arabic":"وَأَنَّ إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ ٱلۡمُنتَهَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4826,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-anna ilā rabbika al-muntahā ","translations":["And that","to","your Lord","(is) the final goal","(42)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-anna","ilā","rabbika","al-muntahā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1450],[2,1450,2110],[3,2110,3060],[4,3060,5375]]}},{"name":"53:43","price":"तथा यह कि निःसंदह वही है, जिसने हँसाया तथा रुलाया।","arabic":"وَأَنَّهُۥ هُوَ أَضۡحَكَ وَأَبۡكَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4827,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-annahu huwa aḍḥaka wa-abkā ","translations":["And that He","[He]","makes (one) laugh","and makes (one) weep","(43)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-annahu","huwa","aḍḥaka","wa-abkā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1850],[2,1850,2270],[3,2270,3270],[4,3270,4385]]}},{"name":"53:44","price":"तथा यह कि निःसंदेह वही है, जिसने मृत्यु दी और जीवन दिया।","arabic":"وَأَنَّهُۥ هُوَ أَمَاتَ وَأَحۡيَا","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4828,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-annahu huwa amāta wa-aḥyā ","translations":["And that He","[He]","causes death","and gives life","(44)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-annahu","huwa","amāta","wa-aḥyā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1950],[2,1950,2300],[3,2300,3320],[4,3320,4525]]}},{"name":"53:45","price":"और यह कि निःसंदेह उसी ने दो प्रकार : नर और मादा पैदा किए।","arabic":"وَأَنَّهُۥ خَلَقَ ٱلزَّوۡجَيۡنِ ٱلذَّكَرَ وَٱلۡأُنثَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4829,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-annahu khalaqa al-zawjayni al-dhakara wal-unthā ","translations":["And that He","created","the pairs","the male","and the female","(45)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-annahu","khalaqa","al-zawjayni","al-dhakara","wal-unthā",null],"verseT