का स्वामी अल्लाह है।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-annahu huwa rabbu al-shiʿ'rā ","translations":["And that He","[He]","(is the) Lord","(of) Sirius","(49)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-annahu","huwa","rabbu","al-shiʿ'rā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1770],[2,1770,2140],[3,2140,2850],[4,2850,4415]]}},{"name":"53:50","price":"और यह कि निःसंदेह उसी ने प्रथम 'आद' [14] को विनष्ट किया।","arabic":"وَأَنَّهُۥٓ أَهۡلَكَ عَادًا ٱلۡأُولَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4834,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"14. यह हूद (अलैहिस्सलाम) की जाति थे।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-annahu ahlaka ʿādan al-ūlā ","translations":["And that He","destroyed","Aad","the first","(50)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-annahu","ahlaka","ʿādan","al-ūlā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2950],[2,2950,3840],[3,3840,4660],[4,4660,5935]]}},{"name":"53:51","price":"तथा समूद को, फिर (किसी को) बाक़ी न छोड़ा।","arabic":"وَثَمُودَاْ فَمَآ أَبۡقَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4835,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wathamūdā famā abqā ","translations":["And Thamud","so not","He spared","(51)"],"transliterationArr":["wathamūdā","famā","abqā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1150],[2,1150,3500],[3,3500,4855]]}},{"name":"53:52","price":"तथा इनसे पहले नूह़ की जाति को। निःसंदेह वे बहुत ही ज़ालिम और बड़े ही सरकश थे।","arabic":"وَقَوۡمَ نُوحٖ مِّن قَبۡلُۖ إِنَّهُمۡ كَانُواْ هُمۡ أَظۡلَمَ وَأَطۡغَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4836,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"waqawma nūḥin min qablu innahum kānū hum aẓlama wa-aṭghā ","translations":["And (the) people","(of) Nuh","before","before","Indeed, they","they were","they were","more unjust","and more rebellious","(52)"],"transliterationArr":["waqawma","nūḥin","min","qablu","innahum","kānū","hum","aẓlama","wa-aṭghā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,890],[2,890,1580],[3,1580,3870],[4,3870,4820],[5