you laugh","and (do) not","weep","(60)"],"transliterationArr":["wataḍḥakūna","walā","tabkūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1670],[2,1670,2250],[3,2250,5625]]}},{"name":"53:61","price":"तथा तुम ग़ाफ़िल हो!","arabic":"وَأَنتُمۡ سَٰمِدُونَ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4845,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-antum sāmidūna ","translations":["While you","amuse (yourselves)","(61)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-antum","sāmidūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2090],[2,2090,5975]]}},{"name":"53:62","price":"अतः अल्लाह को सजदा करो और उसी की इबादत[18] करो।","arabic":"فَٱسۡجُدُواْۤ لِلَّهِۤ وَٱعۡبُدُواْ۩","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4846,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"18. ह़दीस में है कि जब सजदे की प्रथम सूरत \"नज्म\" उतरी, तो नबी (सल्लल्लाहु अलैहि व सल्लम) और जो आपके पास थे, सब ने सजदा किया, एक व्यक्ति के सिवा। उसने कुछ धूल ली, और उसपर सज्दा किया। तो मैंने इसके पश्चात् देखा कि वह काफ़िर रहते हुए मारा गया। और वह उमय्या बिन ख़लफ़ है। (सह़ीह़ बुख़ारी : 4863)","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-us'judū lillahi wa-uʿ'budū ","translations":["So prostrate","to Allah","and worship (Him)","(62)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-us'judū","lillahi","wa-uʿ'budū",""],"verseTiming":[[1,0,930],[2,930,2380],[3,2380,3735]]}}],"chapter":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm","Chapter An-Najm","Najm","Surah Najm","Chapter Najm","An Najm","Surah An Najm","Chapter An Najm","Surah 53","Chapter 53","The Star","النجم"],"version":{"key":"hindi_omari","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"hi","version":"1.1.4","last_update":1675069101,"title":"Hindi Translation","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Indian by Azizul-Haqq Al-Umary."}}